SEARCH
Package grafioschtrader.reportviews.securitycurrency

Interface ISecurityDataProviderUrls

All Known Implementing Classes:
SecuritycurrencyPosition, SecurityDataProviderUrls
public interface ISecurityDataProviderUrls
Interface for objects that hold data provider URLs for securities and currency pairs. These URLs provide access to external data sources for historical prices, intraday prices, dividends, and stock splits. Implementing classes include: - SecuritycurrencyPosition - used in watchlist and portfolio reports - SecurityDataProviderUrls - standalone DTO for API responses
